      "date": "2018-11-19 19:28:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-47vm6: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d171c63d-569c-46a6-b208-08190face660 ran 4 tests.",
